              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Fast neutron fluxes were measured by removing the large",
                "plastic scintillator and observing the induced Au-198",
                "activity in gold foils placed around the tritium sample",
                "From the known Au-197(n,gamma)Au-198 cross sections",
                "and from the calculated neutron energy spectrum from a",
                "lithium target thick enough to stop the proton beam,",
                "the total flux of neutrons in the energy range",
                "30-1200 keV was calculated."
              ]
            }
          ],
